12.21	Mai_lai	My Lai Massacre	The massacre took place in the hamlets of Mỹ Lai and My Khe of Sơn Mỹ village. The event is also known as the Sơn Mỹ Massacre (Vietnamese: ) or sometimes as the Song Mỹ Massacre. The US military codeword for the "Viet Gong stronghold" was "Pinkville".	http://upload.wikimedia.org/wikipedia/commons/thumb/7/77/My_Lai_massacre.jpg/220px-My_Lai_massacre.jpg
